{"tid":2068935,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"其實電視劇大趨勢係咪 半粒鐘 一集？","createTime":"2020-06-18T04:49:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T06:48:38.000Z","uid":61443,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b31dbdc0ea4d29fb99385ea2f5e9bf4aa1a3e4a5","tid":2068935,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:49:23.000Z","msg":"2020年 <br />\n<br />\n1. 草根工時<br />\n唔止香港人<br />\n全球都愈嚟愈長<br />\n瞓都唔夠瞓<br />\n1粒鍾係好大成本<br />\n<br />\n2. 即食文化<br />\n手機一日都唔夠時間玩<br />\n仲有 ps5 , VR館.... 等等新類型視覺刺激 <br />\n最緊要短時間就嚟料 <br />\n<br />\n3. 廣告<br />\n而家唔駛電視台都睇到劇集<br />\n一粒鍾係因為增加咗廣告時段<br />\n而家賣廣告方式唔同<br />\n唔駛再一粒鍾<br />\n<br />\n我對劇集睇法 (2020年)<br />\n隨身睇 + 任何時間睇 + 半粒鍾<br />\n未來仲加入 互動玩法"},{"pid":"ebcae323ac008901ce1df3639a0fe5637bd38b6a","tid":2068935,"uid":307619,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:50:43.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足 2<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068918</a></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"dbabdca2bc2f4ccbb11966374d2ee40e9f2c62d2","tid":2068935,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:18:58.000Z","msg":"愛回家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b968d6693e35428aad812a0960a81cc1c7e82ca","tid":2068935,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"dbabdca2bc2f4ccbb11966374d2ee40e9f2c62d2","tid":2068935,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:18:58.000Z","msg":"愛回家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T06:23:56.000Z","msg":"半粒鍾唔一定愛回家 <br />\n<br />\n主題要鮮明 <br />\n節奏要明快 <br />\n<br />\n其實最緊要個節奏 <br />\n要開始拍得住電影 <br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講要好睇編劇能力"},{"pid":"2a4c7c33b04b917a37982bb48355e81b0f10ad6b","tid":2068935,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T06:53:08.000Z","msg":"邊到有愈黎愈長？"},{"pid":"be6e9b6105c6fbd637e322dd1db3073b4ee5872f","tid":2068935,"uid":66893,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b968d6693e35428aad812a0960a81cc1c7e82ca","tid":2068935,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"dbabdca2bc2f4ccbb11966374d2ee40e9f2c62d2","tid":2068935,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:18:58.000Z","msg":"愛回家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T06:23:56.000Z","msg":"半粒鍾唔一定愛回家 <br />\n<br />\n主題要鮮明 <br />\n節奏要明快 <br />\n<br />\n其實最緊要個節奏 <br />\n要開始拍得住電影 <br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講要好睇編劇能力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T07:07:24.000Z","msg":"外國劇集黎講 run, i may destroy you, normal people, 甚至 the mandalorian都係半個鐘一集"},{"pid":"8e46f95d8662576d6f6abbaa09584bb582f8a944","tid":2068935,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be6e9b6105c6fbd637e322dd1db3073b4ee5872f","tid":2068935,"u